query:
INSERT INTO paper_trading_sessions (strategy_id, credential_id, status, initial_balance, current_balance, started_at, updated_at)
        VALUES ($1, $2, 'running', $3, $3, NOW(), NOW())
        ON CONFLICT (strategy_id) DO UPDATE SET
            credential_id = $2,
            status = 'running',
            initial_balance = $3,
            current_balance = $3,
            started_at = NOW(),
            updated_at = NOW()
